# FAQ
## Server Questions

### What's the server about?
SnR Season 2 is a Nations SMP, focusing on centralized production, rail transport, community building, and light lore.
### Where do I download the modpack?
Check the “download” section.
### How do I join the server?
Click the “Steam ‘n Rails SMP” button on the game’s main menu.
### Where can I find the rules?
Check the “rules” section.
### My pack crashed! Help?
Send us a crash log in #crash-reports on the server. 



## Nation Questions

### What's a nation?
Nations are collections of players who have banded together for various reasons. There are benefits to being in a nation, such as funding for projects, easier access to materials, and so on. Nations contain guilds and businesses, and provide benefits to them while also benefiting from their trade.
### How do I join a nation?
Ask its leaders! Most nations will accept new members.
How do I make a nation?
You will need a group of other players, land to build on, exports to make you money… it's a process. 
